OL,3,CElectric vehicle drivers face London
OL,4,Ccongestion charge for first time
OL,6,FElectric vehicle (EV) drivers in
OL,7,Fcentral London have to pay the
OL,8,Fcapital's congestion charge for the
OL,9,Ffirst time.
OL,11,FMayor Sir Sadiq Khan confirmed in
OL,12,FNovember that EVs would lose their
OL,13,Fexemption from the fee.
OL,15,FThe regular daily congestion charge
OL,16,Ffor non-electrified vehicles has also
OL,17,Frisen for the first time since 2020 `
OL,18,Ffrom #15 to #18.
