OL,3,CElectric vehicle drivers face London
OL,4,Ccongestion charge for first time
OL,6,FReductions of up to 90% will be
OL,7,Fawarded to residents who live within
OL,8,Fthe zone.
OL,10,FHowever, those who move into the zone
OL,11,Fafter March 1 2027 will not get a
OL,12,Fdiscount unless they use an electric
OL,13,Fvehicle.
OL,15,FIt comes ahead of so-called manic
OL,16,FMonday, the first working Monday of
OL,17,Fthe year which is expected to be one
OL,18,Fof the worst days for breakdowns.
